jpg\\/65b81b41-4249-420c-a1fa-448fb3bc23aa?t=1691758508436\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>K&ecirc;nh Tiktok &ldquo;H\\u1ed3ng sinh vi&ecirc;n&rdquo; livestream qu\\u1ea3ng b&aacute; v&agrave; ti&ecirc;u th\\u1ee5 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch&egrave; c\\u1ee7a v&ugrave;ng ch&egrave; La B\\u1eb1ng, \\u0110\\u1ea1i T\\u1eeb<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cms.thainguyen.vn\\/documents\\/130230\\/12411398\\/Anh+6.jpg\\/33b88ce3-3e9f-48c5-b33b-5b54f95fa23a?t=1691758508473\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Ch\\u1ee7 k&ecirc;nh tiktok n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng &ldquo;\\u1ea8m th\\u1ef1c m\\u1eb9 l&agrave;m&rdquo; \\u0110\\u1ed3ng Tr\\u1ecdng H&ugrave;ng (&aacute;o tr\\u1eafng) c&ugrave;ng m\\u1eb9 tham gia Phi&ecirc;n ch\\u1ee3<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cms.thainguyen.vn\\/documents\\/130230\\/12411398\\/Anh+7.jpg\\/479c044b-b55b-4fb9-9e4d-59b241348d80?t=1691758509165\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m na c\\u1ee7a huy\\u1ec7n v&ugrave;ng cao V&otilde; Nhai \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c qu\\u1ea3ng b&aacute; v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1ef1c kh&aacute;ch quan t&acirc;m t\\u1ea1i phi&ecirc;n livestream<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cms.thainguyen.vn\\/documents\\/130230\\/12411398\\/Anh+8.jpg\\/d4f6fd53-f3fd-4c5c-8bce-95d5d998db74?t=1691758509646\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>\\u0110\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n c&aacute;c h\\u1ee3p t&aacute;c x&atilde; vui m\\u1eebng khi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tham gia Phi&ecirc;n ch\\u1ee3 n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t v&agrave; hy v\\u1ecdng \\u0111&acirc;y s\\u1ebd l&agrave; h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111i m\\u1edbi trong qu\\u1ea3ng b&aacute; n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng (Trong \\u1ea3nh: Ch\\u1ecb Ho&agrave;ng Th\\u1ecb T&acirc;n, Gi&aacute;m \\u0111\\u1ed1c H\\u1ee3p t&aacute;c x&atilde; T&acirc;m Tr&agrave; Th&aacute;i qu\\u1ea3ng