(753, '1', 'sc_admin/page/edit/9a5b28c4-3a1a-4d28-8719-8c2feb1febd5', 'POST', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/118.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '{\"descriptions\":{\"vi\":{\"title\":\"Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u\",\"keyword\":null,\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<p>Trang th&ocirc;ng tin k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i cung c\\u1ea7u s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n, th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m an to&agrave;n l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t k&ecirc;nh giao th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ec1 n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n, th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m an to&agrave;n. \\u1ede \\u0111&oacute; t\\u1eeb c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, h\\u1ed9 gia \\u0111&igrave;nh nh\\u1ecf l\\u1ebb t\\u1edbi doanh nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n, th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m an to&agrave;n c&oacute; c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i tham gia g\\u1eb7p g\\u1ee1, k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i, gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v&agrave; kinh doanh; c\\u01a1 quan qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute; c&aacute;c c\\u1ea5p ph&aacute;t huy vai tr&ograve; gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t, x\\u1eed l&yacute; vi ph\\u1ea1m \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o th&ocirc;ng tin trung th\\u1ef1c, l&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 tin c\\u1eady \\u0111\\u1ec3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1edbi. T\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u cu\\u1ed1i c&ugrave;ng \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; khuy\\u1ebfn kh&iacute;ch s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh c&aacute;c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ea3m v\\u1ec7 sinh an to&agrave;n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m, b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf ng&agrave;nh n&ocirc;ng nghi\\u1ec7p.<br \\/>\\r\\nH\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u01b0a ra k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 \\u0111&aacute;nh gi&aacute;, x\\u1ebfp h\\u1ea1ng c&aacute;c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m, doanh nghi\\u1ec7p uy t&iacute;n th&ocirc;ng qua b&igrave;nh ch\\u1ecdn c\\u1ee7a c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u \\u0111&oacute; c&oacute; ngh\\u0129a, vi\\u1ec7c tham gia v&agrave;o h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng K\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i cung c\\u1ea7u n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n, th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m an to&agrave;n l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 x&aacute;c th\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 v\\u1ec1 an to&agrave;n v\\u1ec7 sinh th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m.<br \\/>\\r\\nTuy nhi&ecirc;n, \\u0111i\\u1ec3m kh&aacute;c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a trang th&ocirc;ng tin n&agrave;y so v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c s&agrave;n giao d\\u1ecbch th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed kh&aacute;c \\u0111&oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; vai tr&ograve; c\\u1ee7a c&aacute;c c\\u01a1 quan qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute; Nh&agrave; n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o: m\\u1eb7t h&agrave;ng g&igrave;, c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb n&agrave;o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tham gia l&ecirc;n h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng. Vi\\u1ec7c n&agrave;y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o th&ocirc;ng qua Quy ch\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v&agrave; c\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf x&aacute;c th\\u1ef1c c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng, v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 tham gia gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t c\\u1ee7a c\\u01a1 quan ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v&agrave; s\\u1edf ban ng&agrave;nh c\\u1ea5p t\\u1ec9nh.<br \\/>\\r\\nTrang th&ocirc;ng tin \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng d\\u1ef1a tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i v&agrave; h\\u1ea1 t\\u1ea7ng CNTT-VT ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf d\\u1ec5 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, th&acirc;n thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng, c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 khai th&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh, c&aacute;c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1edbi t&iacute;nh c\\u01a1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, linh ho\\u1ea1t cao, mang l\\u1ea1i nhi\\u1ec1u th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; l\\u1ee3i &iacute;ch, thu h&uacute;t ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute;, c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng khai th&aacute;c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.<br \\/>\\r\\nM\\u1ecdi c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c, c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh \\u0111\\u1ec1u c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u0103ng k&yacute; th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c\\u1ee7a trang th&ocirc;ng tin k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i cung c\\u1ea7u n&ocirc;ng s\\u1ea3n, th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m an to&agrave;n. Vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u0103ng k&yacute; th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng l&agrave; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n mi\\u1ec5n ph&iacute;.<br \\/>\\r\\nC&aacute; nh&acirc;n, t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c, c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u0103ng k&yacute; th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n qua: \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 email, t&agrave;i kho\\u1ea3n facebook, t&agrave;i kho\\u1ea3n google, s\\u1ed1 \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i.<br \\/>\\r\\nUBND t\\u1ec9nh Th&aacute;i Nguy&ecirc;n&nbsp;ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi t\\u1eadp \\u0111o&agrave;n VNPT x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng n&agrave;y nh\\u1eb1m m\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;G&oacute;p ph\\u1ea7n gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 v\\u1ec1 an to&agrave;n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m hi\\u1ec7n nay: Cung c\\u1ea5p cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 tin c\\u1eady, c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 th&ocirc;ng tin \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1ea1t ti&ecirc;u chu\\u1ea9n s\\u1ea1ch, an to&agrave;n, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe cho c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng. T\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng &nbsp;s\\u1ef1 qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute;, gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t c\\u1ee7a c\\u01a1 quan Nh&agrave; n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 an to&agrave;n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m t\\u1eeb kh&acirc;u s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh \\u0111\\u1ebfn ti&ecirc;u th\\