rc;y ch&egrave; \\u0111\\u1ea1t n\\u0103ng su\\u1ea5t cao, nh\\u01b0ng gi&aacute; b&aacute;n l\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea3m li&ecirc;n t\\u1ee5c.&nbsp;<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>C&ograve;n n\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ch&egrave; c\\u1ee7a gia \\u0111&igrave;nh ch\\u1ecb Tr\\u1ea7n Th\\u1ecb Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u0103m s&oacute;c theo quy tr&igrave;nh s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch&egrave; an to&agrave;n sinh h\\u1ecdc ti&ecirc;u chu\\u1ea9n VietGap n&ecirc;n v\\u1ee5 ch&egrave; n\\u0103m 2019 n&agrave;y, \\u0111\\u1ed3i ch&egrave; nh&agrave; ch\\u1ecb cho n\\u0103ng su\\u1ea5t b&igrave;nh qu&acirc;n kho\\u1ea3ng 20 t\\u1ea5n\\/ha. Tuy n\\u0103ng su\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ea1t cao h\\u01a1n n\\u0103m ngo&aacute;i xong gi&aacute; b&aacute;n th\\u1ea5p n&ecirc;n thu nh\\u1eadp c\\u1ee7a gia \\u0111&igrave;nh ch\\u1ecb v\\u1eabn ch\\u1ec9 b\\u1eb1ng n\\u0103m tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc, t\\u1ee9c l&agrave; kho\\u1ea3ng 30 tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ed3ng. Gi&aacute; ch&egrave; b&uacute;p t\\u01b0\\u01a1i xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5p l&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n do khi\\u1ebfn ch\\u1ecb Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v&agrave; nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u1ed9 tr\\u1ed3ng ch&egrave; kh&aacute;c \\u1edf B\\u1ea3n Xen ph&aacute; v\\u1ee1 h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u0111&atilde; k&yacute; k\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi C&ocirc;ng Ty c\\u1ed5 ph\\u1ea7n ch&egrave; Thanh B&igrave;nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Su\\u1ed1t nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m qua, 98% s\\u1ed1 ch&egrave; thu mua t\\u1eeb nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0323c C&ocirc;ng ty C\\u1ed5 ph\\u1ea7n ch&egrave; Thanh B&igrave;nh xu&acirc;\\u0301t kh&acirc;\\u0309u sang thi\\u0323 tr\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0300ng \\u0110a\\u0300i Loan (Trung Qu\\u1ed1c) va\\u0300 Trung \\u0110&ocirc;ng&hellip; Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, t\\u1eeb v\\u1ee5 ch&egrave; n\\u0103m 2018, ta\\u0323i vu\\u0300ng che\\u0300 nguy&ecirc;n li&ecirc;\\u0323u huy&ecirc;\\u0323n M\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0300ng Kh\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111&atilde; xa\\u0309y ra ti\\u0300nh tra\\u0323ng ca\\u0323nh tranh thu mua nguy&ecirc;n li&ecirc;\\u0323u gi\\u01b0\\u0303a ca\\u0301c ti&ecirc;\\u0309u th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, doanh nghi&ecirc;\\u0323p ngoa\\u0300i \\u0111i\\u0323a ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n&agrave;y \\u0111&atilde; g&acirc;y kh&oacute; kh\\u0103n cho C&ocirc;ng ty c\\u1ed5 ph\\u1ea7n ch&egrave; Thanh B&igrave;nh trong vi\\u1ec7c bao ti&ecirc;u s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m v&agrave; qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute; v&ugrave;ng nguy&ecirc;n li\\u1ec7u. Th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf n&agrave;y \\u0111&ograve;i h\\u1ecfi m\\u1ed1i li&ecirc;n k\\u1ebft gi\\u1eefa n&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n v\\u1edbi C&ocirc;ng ty Ch&egrave; C\\u1ed5 ph\\u1ea7n Thanh B&igrave;nh trong th\\u1eddi gian t\\u1edbi c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i ch\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ebd h\\u01a1n, sao cho h&agrave;i h&ograve;a l\\u1ee3i &iacute;ch \\u1edf c\\u1ea3 02 ph&iacute;a: Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t kinh doanh c&oacute; l&atilde;i v&agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea1i, b&agrave; con n&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n c&oacute; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ngu\\u1ed3n thu \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t\\u1eeb c&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed3i ch&egrave;.<\\/p>\"}},\"category_id\":\"9a674ced-85a0-44d2-a51e-0eb36ec47d4e\",\"alias\":\"can-thua-mua-gom-che-tuoi\",\"image\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/3_7.png\",\"sort\":\"0\",\"status\":\"on\",\"_token\":\"jZySFJVtsHmuFGyxtC51GlNSRQvPtD0qhb2MwgKT\"}', '2023-10-21 02:10:15', '2023-10-21 02:10:15'),
